# Knowledge base — plan-b-cli

This repo is part of the **apito** ecosystem inside a submodule monorepo.

Read before coding:
1. `.knowledge/README.md` — this repo's purpose, architecture, decisions.
2. `.memory/CURRENT.md` and `.memory/HANDOFF.md` — current working state.
3. The monorepo root `.knowledge/README.md`, `.knowledge/ABOUT_ME.md`, `.knowledge/WORKFLOW.md` — global rules & the AI contract.

`.knowledge/` = durable truth; `.memory/` = ephemeral working state.
At session end, update `.memory/` (CURRENT, HANDOFF, CHANGELOG_AI) per the root WORKFLOW.md.
Never hand-edit generated code; never commit secrets/builds/node_modules.
